Package: r6x
Type: Package
Title: Extensions to the R6 package
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-04-02
Authors@R: person("Janko", "Thyson", email = "janko.thyson@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Facilitates the creation of formal S4 equivalents for R6 classes
    and provides a base layer object for inheritance featuring basic methods
    such as `.getFieldNames()` and `.getMethodNames()` that seem to be
    required often.
URL: http://github.com/rappster/r6x
BugReports: http://github.com/rappster/r6x/issues
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: R6
VignetteBuilder: knitr
